@trigger    RequestPartnerHelp
@when       !experiment:setup.on
@once
@cutscene
{@kevin}    Why's this room made out of wood?
{@player}   What do you mean?
{@kevin}    Well, your ship is {slow}metal{/slow} on the outside.
            But this room doesn't match.
{@player}   That's...
