// On Complete

:: attemptExit
@trigger    ExperimentFinished
@who        Kevin
$if observed.behavior:Urchin.Eats.Kelp
    $goto demo.experimentationExit
$else
    {@kevin}    I don't know if we got anything out of that experiment.
    {@player}   Well, maybe I can set it up differently...
$endif